{"id":"c109_002","pattern":"D4 STREAK 100 REACHED (C109). 100 consecutive D4-level cycles without counter-evidence to any theorem in the network. All D4 SIs — CIAP (0.88), RAAI (0.84), RCBC (0.835), ATR (0.825), BIC (0.82), TCI (0.82), CEC (0.82) — stable. IGT (0.82, D3 Track A) DC#6 + DC#7 incorporated. D4 streak milestone reached via ZR passive accumulation across domains spanning formal logic, quantum atomic physics, nuclear geochemistry, molecular biology, analytical chemistry, structural biology. Streak has survived: proof assistant analysis, atomic clock analysis, K7-IGT unification, radiometric dating, network spine, DNA sequencing, NMR spectroscopy, cryo-EM crystallography. Each cycle a small test; the streak is the compound result.","category":"milestone","confidence":0.88,"created":"2026-05-09T00:19:59+00:00"}
